会议，在相关领域具有较高学术影响力。]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">喻莉教授在同济医药卫生管理学院的学术论坛上做学术报告</title><link href="https://hustdmin.github.io/blog/2024/tongji/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="喻莉教授在同济医药卫生管理学院的学术论坛上做学术报告"/><published>2024-11-13T14:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2024-11-13T14:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://hustdmin.github.io/blog/2024/tongji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hustdmin.github.io/blog/2024/tongji/"><![CDATA[<p>喻莉教授参与了湖北省长期护理保险筹资与经办服务规程研讨会，在会上以“情智适老——面向适老陪伴的情智交互具身智能体系统开发及应用”为题作报告，详细介绍了基于人体骨架的行为实时感知、时空圈卷积的跌倒算法、无接触式远程心率检测、基于人脸动作单元的情绪检测和情感硅基大模型的拟人交流等技术，并表示这些技术可应用于家庭养老。</p> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 480px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-tongji1-480.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 800px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-tongji1-800.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 1400px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-tongji1-1400.webp"/> <img src="/assets/img/news/2024-tongji1.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="auto" height="auto" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> </div> <div class="row mt-3"> <div class="col-sm mt-3 mt-md-0"> <figure> <picture> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 480px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-tongji2-480.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 800px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-tongji2-800.webp"/> <source class="responsive-img-srcset" media="(max-width: 1400px)" srcset="/assets/img/news/2024-tongji2-1400.webp"/> <img src="/assets/img/news/2024-tongji2.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded z-depth-1" width="auto" height="auto" onerror="this.onerror=null; $('.responsive-img-srcset').remove();"/> </picture> </figure> </div> </div>]]></content><author><name></name></author><category term="讲座"/><summary type="html"><![CDATA[喻莉教授参与了湖北省长期护理保险